Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.78,0:02:13.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(450,0)}反击 的 处刑台
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.84,0:02:24.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.11,0:02:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 所杀的人数已记不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没人会去数刷牙吃饭的次数
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.32,0:02:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.25,0:02:51.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Geass适合暗杀 听别人说的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.38,0:02:52.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我才杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也没别的地方可待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.57,0:02:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入工作？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.98,0:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,演弟弟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能做到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从未见过父母亲人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 若这是命令
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.33,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的哥哥就是鲁路修·兰佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.89,0:03:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的Geass是停止时间的能力吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.99,0:03:19.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没理由回答你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.94,0:03:21.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到的指令是
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.16,0:03:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若鲁路修·兰佩洛奇记忆恢复
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.12,0:03:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若ZERO复活 就将其抹杀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.43,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,16 17 18 19…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.75,0:03:33.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(424,435)\fs22}这数字是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.74,0:03:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从你出现时起 我就在心里计算时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.50,0:03:41.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但现在数字有偏差
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以为是什么原因
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你将成为寻找娜娜莉的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 你停止的并非时间
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.11,0:03:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是我身体所感受到的时间而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.22,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算明白这个也赢不了我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.24,0:04:06.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 谁也不能度过和我相同的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.31,0:04:08.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 你是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.20,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有立即杀了我 就是因为你很清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:16.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去 两样东西都得不到
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.33,0:04:17.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两样？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.17,0:04:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个是你们以我为诱饵正在追寻的C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.81,0:04:24.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若你能放过我 我就把C.C.给你揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.10,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要出卖C.C.吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己的性命最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.56,0:04:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另一个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:32.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的生命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,命算什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 未来是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.46,0:04:39.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来就是希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.35,0:04:42.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的任务前方有希望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓住了C.C. 你能开拓出怎样的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:50.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维持现状而已 一成不变
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:51.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我 就完不成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想抓住C.C.吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天 我会把C.C.揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.16,0:05:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就能抓住崭新的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.39,0:05:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没问题 我不会说谎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.91,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有对你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.17,0:05:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我想起青森来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.90,0:05:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比那好点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少全员都穿了衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO对总领事下了Geass吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.41,0:05:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.89,0:05:25.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过在此失手的话 我们和鲁路修就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又支离破碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真意外
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.29,0:05:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟独自前来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中华联邦的总领事应该已经承认日本合众国了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.03,0:05:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那位大人即将去世
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.74,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团要选择在此毁灭一途吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.58,0:05:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,慢着 突然说这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.35,0:05:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就当总领事在我们手中光荣殉职好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.79,0:05:51.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:54.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO似乎点燃了意外的导火索啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.16,0:05:58.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是远大的理想 还是庸俗的野心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.37,0:06:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姑且争取到了让罗洛等待的时间
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.87,0:06:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若能得到C.C. 他就会隐瞒我恢复记忆的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.64,0:06:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而 他的根本目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.92,0:06:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎不是在布里塔尼亚升迁或对其效忠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:18.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么说 该寻找别的线索吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽是危险的牌 但有相应的价值
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.29,0:06:23.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没时间踌躇了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:27.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天藤堂他们就会被处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.47,0:06:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.58,0:06:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的Geass已暴露给罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算想办法杀了罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.86,0:06:35.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我记忆恢复的事也会被机情知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样的话娜娜莉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在救出娜娜莉之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.56,0:06:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有继续假装学生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:46.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好 吉尔弗德等人似乎和机情联系不深
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.73,0:06:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隐藏的Knightmare未被发现也能说明
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.74,0:06:54.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.49,0:06:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:07:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同时除去罗洛的方法…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:08.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难以接受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.99,0:07:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那小鬼杀了布鲁诺吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.69,0:07:13.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是第五人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,维克多也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过碰到了他的挂坠盒就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.91,0:07:18.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那人平时就有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.13,0:07:20.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但也不至于被杀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.30,0:07:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自称ZERO的人都出现了 我们必须更团结
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.29,0:07:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟杀害同伴的死神 要怎么组队啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组队？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:33.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是任务吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要什么同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.58,0:07:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活的ZERO是那个ZERO吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.69,0:07:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:45.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是哪个 都会再度抛弃我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.83,0:07:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总领事馆的爆炸事件原因呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今还没有官方说明
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.58,0:07:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是有联络说认可执行处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处刑不过是以儆效尤
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.07,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我来说是低级的手段
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.16,0:08:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会出现吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.30,0:08:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出来的话也好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.86,0:08:08.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无意引发奇迹的ZERO 也得不到民众支持
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.52,0:08:10.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您连这一步都想到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 我希望他出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.68,0:08:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是祈祷他出现
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.37,0:08:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了不知身在何处的公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.69,0:08:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您为何承认日本合众国
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.16,0:08:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还未向朱禁城确认就独断专行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是大宦官之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.25,0:08:32.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这行为也不可饶恕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.41,0:08:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使您打算利用ZERO…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎可利用ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有ZERO才有幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.82,0:08:42.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣上的圣意呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.35,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那种小丫头哪比得上ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO会赐予我幸福才是绝对的法则
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.61,0:08:50.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这卖国贼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.29,0:08:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,红天已死
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.14,0:08:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.45,0:09:01.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论杀害 情报操作还是伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.69,0:09:03.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走哪条路罗洛都是瓶颈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,处刑开始之前必须想办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.18,0:09:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到那情报的证据
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.09,0:09:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去曾自称黑色骑士团
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.03,0:09:21.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扰乱11区的恐怖分子的处刑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.99,0:09:24.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在即将执行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.25,0:09:27.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO会现身于部下的刑场之上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人 求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.25,0:09:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救救藤堂将军
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别杀他们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.13,0:09:41.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO背叛了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.26,0:09:42.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会来救我们的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.79,0:09:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要那是本人 只要他还活着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:48.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定会来引发奇迹的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:50.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奇迹…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:52.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别放松警戒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.48,0:09:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然可能性很低
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但C.C.也有可能出现
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.33,0:10:02.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇要…这下就结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.29,0:10:07.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来吧 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.81,0:10:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,父亲安德列斯·达尔顿的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.31,0:10:14.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部队发来机密指令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.26,0:10:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为防止通信窃听 命属下口头传达
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.51,0:10:25.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的身份 我暂借一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这该怎么理解才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.39,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若ZERO出现 只管行动便是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.92,0:10:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算我们对布里塔尼亚开炮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.75,0:10:38.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也可以装作一无所知？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:40.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想这交易不算坏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说你是武官
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.84,0:10:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来搞政治也挺有一套啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金梅尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:48.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先行量产机没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:52.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机情使用过 说不定会有奇怪的坏习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是重要的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.90,0:10:56.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一点不对劲就立即报告
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.80,0:10:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是金梅尔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:11:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent无异常 可以出击
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.39,0:11:03.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若不遵守约定 就杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:07.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.95,0:11:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 终于到了处刑时间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.62,0:11:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团残党即将接受正义的制裁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:15.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求您
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:18.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请显示奇迹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11区人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.70,0:11:23.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们所相信的ZERO没有现身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.64,0:11:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都是骗局
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.20,0:11:29.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他逃避了我提出的堂堂正正的决斗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.15,0:11:30.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,举枪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:37.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.23,0:11:38.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.26,0:11:41.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这里出去你也会被杀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.22,0:11:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.54,0:11:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,够了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.86,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已做得够好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不对
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:50.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你错了 吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.70,0:11:52.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他来了 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.82,0:11:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们也无法出手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办 凭你一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.93,0:11:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.30,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绕到后面了吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.36,0:12:08.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吉尔弗德 你即将处刑的不是恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.95,0:12:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我合众国军 黑色骑士团的士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.88,0:12:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要我根据国际法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.64,0:12:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承认他们是俘虏？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.13,0:12:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.38,0:12:18.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然出现了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.61,0:12:20.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 若打破了与我的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.98,0:12:22.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就要死 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.54,0:12:25.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 鲁路修·兰佩洛奇
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------TXTB------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:36.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO现身了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多么愚蠢的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.19,0:12:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.26,0:12:41.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.37,0:12:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是本人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还用说吗 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.53,0:12:50.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然有公布处刑的事 但没有更多报导啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.27,0:12:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.63,0:12:52.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.44,0:12:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO只有一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.69,0:12:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然乘在Knightmare Frame上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:57.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目的应该不是自首吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.05,0:12:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是若打算独自一人作战…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看 我说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.99,0:13:05.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 就按去年的计划行事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.75,0:13:09.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那得等ZERO先渡过这难关才行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.08,0:13:11.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咲世子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了今后的打算 先开始进行那个准备吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.21,0:13:17.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚军方面已开始…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.70,0:13:18.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.81,0:13:20.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有罗洛跟着
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.26,0:13:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,半小时前就进了螺旋剧场
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久违了 吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.35,0:13:29.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出来叙叙旧如何
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.71,0:13:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,承蒙邀请 不过请容我谢绝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.65,0:13:36.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,过去的因缘 让我以Knightmare来回应吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.58,0:13:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不出来就无法使用Geass
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:40.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你的风格
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.45,0:13:42.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么来确定规则吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.24,0:13:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,规则？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.17,0:13:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,决斗的规则
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.48,0:13:49.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战斗要一对一做个了断
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.42,0:13:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我不会让别人插手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.67,0:13:53.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武器只有一件
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.04,0:13:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.33,0:13:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的武器是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.19,0:14:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 让我借那面盾一用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.16,0:14:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么 那是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,镇压暴动用的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.46,0:14:10.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该不会 一开始就
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.29,0:14:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打算自我了断吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.20,0:14:15.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真令人失望 ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.54,0:14:17.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.68,0:14:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能解决一只寄生虫大宦官 算是欠他个人情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.22,0:14:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是 这不是基于永续调和的盟约
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:27.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若ZERO无能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.86,0:14:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只得让黑色骑士团变成外交的工具了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.98,0:14:34.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提个问题 吉尔弗德卿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.24,0:14:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若有正义无法击败的邪恶存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你会如何做
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.29,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不惜玷污双手以恶制恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是宁可舍身取义 也要将自己的正义贯彻到底
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.58,0:14:49.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论如何 留存下来的终究是邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.80,0:14:51.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,矛盾 文字游戏吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的正义与公主殿下同在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.88,0:14:56.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.14,0:14:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若是我 不惜化身为邪恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.53,0:15:00.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也要击杀极恶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,YES Your Highness
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.65,0:15:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.59,0:15:12.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,地震？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.53,0:15:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 这作战是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.81,0:15:16.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色叛乱时的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第12步兵部队
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.42,0:15:26.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去第4等级的阶层控制室
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.98,0:15:27.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO的部下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.38,0:15:29.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指挥突击
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:31.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.93,0:15:34.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自在战斗装甲机部队跟我来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:36.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救出扇先生等人为最优先事项
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,α4呼叫α1 请回答 α1 α1
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:42.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 有人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.98,0:15:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卑鄙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.43,0:15:50.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么一对一啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.52,0:15:55.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巴特
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,黑色骑士团啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.90,0:16:03.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敌人已落入我国领土内
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:06.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快摧毁布里塔尼亚军 拯救同胞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.92,0:16:07.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同胞…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.64,0:16:11.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反过来利用了租界构造吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 在布里塔尼亚重整态势之前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.12,0:16:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解放所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.62,0:16:18.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会被他们逃进中华联邦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.09,0:16:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的目的归根到底是C.C.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.95,0:16:24.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边交给吉尔弗德
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这恐怖分子
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.14,0:16:29.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里已经是日本的领土了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日本是不存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才讨厌布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.27,0:16:42.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了 11区的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,挡住了？在这个距离
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是辐射波动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:54.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,近身后我的胜利就已成定局
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.27,0:16:56.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.62,0:17:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟敢把阿尔弗雷德
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.12,0:17:05.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.16,0:17:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是中华联邦的治外法权区
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.30,0:17:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.14,0:17:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有媒体的摄影机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.68,0:17:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Vincent突击了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.94,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边不能动 快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.62,0:17:32.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.66,0:17:34.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了吗 罗洛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.29,0:17:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然要逃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.10,0:17:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,交出C.C.的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:45.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修 一开始就欺骗了我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.69,0:17:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还不行 还不能被抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说要给我未来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:54.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能死在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要完成任务 就有未来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.05,0:18:03.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,物理现象停止不了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.70,0:18:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直接命中线路
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.91,0:18:17.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 戴维德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,若打中总领事馆 就要跟中华联邦开战了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.21,0:18:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.12,0:18:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:30.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么 要救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:32.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为 你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.95,0:18:35.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是被移植的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.45,0:18:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你共同度过的那段时间 并无虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:43.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至今为止的生活 不是虚假
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你是我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.14,0:18:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.53,0:18:50.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那一天 没有生日的我第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.37,0:18:56.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收到那个
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.92,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明说了 自己的性命最重要
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.64,0:19:02.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却为了那种无聊的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:04.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.80,0:19:06.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的崭新未来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的未来 和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:13.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ZERO 在此了断吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃我一击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:18.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以这铁锤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.65,0:19:27.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么意思 金梅尔卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.60,0:19:29.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.78,0:19:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道 你是ZERO的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.95,0:19:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.68,0:19:35.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲁路修死了任务就…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.34,0:19:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.68,0:19:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛 糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是维蕾塔老师打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用IMOpen（即时通信公开线路）连接
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.32,0:19:50.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛吗 你去哪儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.02,0:19:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讨厌啦 老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.73,0:19:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上个厕所好歹让我们分别解决啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.37,0:19:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 刚才怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.83,0:20:00.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总领事馆的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 好像很轰动啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.60,0:20:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟糕 若之前的事被知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:07.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会被机情局处决
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.08,0:20:09.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个人也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.95,0:20:10.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.75,0:20:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会再让弟弟卷进危险的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是当然的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.68,0:20:19.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,罗洛不适合杀人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.93,0:20:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到此为止 布里塔尼亚的各位
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.05,0:20:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更进一步的行动将视为武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,撤退吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:36.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,扇先生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.84,0:20:38.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢 卡莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.67,0:20:42.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤堂先生你们也…太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.08,0:20:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 给你添麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受苦了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.79,0:20:48.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.05,0:20:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那台Knightmare呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.87,0:20:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道 那架机体本是敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.14,0:20:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的机师我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.38,0:20:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他保护了ZERO
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.20,0:21:01.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,至少不是敌人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.85,0:21:05.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明C.C.就在眼前 我却…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.61,0:21:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一开始 在布里塔尼亚就没有安宁
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.62,0:21:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的归宿 在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,落网了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.74,0:21:19.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然把这种资料留在司令室
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.79,0:21:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明除了Geass以外一无所长吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.45,0:21:24.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这玩意里的密码竟能派上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.97,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.81,0:21:27.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,模式D
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.24,0:21:31.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 ZERO的机体取这个轨道时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.83,0:21:34.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后方攻击追逐他的Knightmare
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.26,0:21:36.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后若ZERO逃出
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.38,0:21:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就把对方的Knightmare完全破坏
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.95,0:21:41.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不逃出的话 就原地待机
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.95,0:21:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将娜娜莉取而代之的冒牌货
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.22,0:21:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我榨干你的每一滴血
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再像破抹布一样抛弃
Comment: 0,0:00:00.80,0:00:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//---------------------------------NEXT------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.84,0:23:41.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么罗洛·兰佩洛奇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.47,0:23:43.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要把那家伙当我弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.54,0:23:45.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直令人耻辱到浑身发抖
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.46,0:23:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很遗憾 若你忠实于机情的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就能在那时被狙击而亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.57,0:23:54.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼 只要今后你能成为方便的棋子
